casebody.data:
No. —, original.

Missouri v. Iowa. December 13, 1937. Mr. Roy McKittrick, Attorney General of Missouri, Mr. Frank W. Hayes, Assistant Attorney General, Mr. M. E. Casey, and Ruth L. Waltner for complainant.

The motion for leave to file the Bill of Complaint herein is granted and process is ordered to issue returnable on Monday, February 14, 1938.
